text.tspan: The Open Innovation Toolkit is sourced from best practices across
multiple industries to help you incorporate human-centered
design into your product development process.
Whether you have a design method that has worked
well in distributed teams, or you want to learn more
about the resources already available, the
Open Innovation Toolkit is the place to go.
More than anything, this toolkit is an invitation
to everyone, from developers to advocates, to
share your experiences, methods and ideas
to help build this collective resource that
can help the community learn from each
other and build a better way of integrating
